OL,3,C'Every hit has an impact': the
OL,4,Cirreversible toll of concussions on
OL,5,Crugby players
OL,7,FWhen Andrew Watkins thinks of his
OL,8,Ffriend Cae Trayhern, he mostly
OL,9,Fremembers an outgoing and positive
OL,10,Fperson.
OL,12,FBut he's also forced to reflect on the
OL,13,Ftoll taken on Cae's life by playing
OL,14,Frugby.
OL,16,FThe two first met aged 5 and and grew
OL,17,Fup playing in the same rugby teams.
OL,19,FCae - a naturally talented and rugged
OL,20,Fback rower - was in the senior squad
OL,21,Fat Pontypool by the age of 18.
