OL,3,C'Every hit has an impact': the
OL,4,Cirreversible toll of concussions on
OL,5,Crugby players
OL,7,F"And was just left. It was
OL,8,Fheartbreaking when his parents had to
OL,9,Fgo and find him alone in that
OL,10,Fsituation."
OL,12,FAndrew says Cae suffered "a minimum of
OL,13,F11 concussions" while playing rugby,
OL,14,Fand they were just the ones his family
OL,15,Fand friends knew about.
OL,17,FTowards the end of his playing career,
OL,18,Fhe asked to switch positions - an
OL,19,Findication of the toll he felt the
OL,20,Fgame was taking on his body.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@KO]tD@ZOUuD@OO]
