OL,3,C'Every hit has an impact': the
OL,4,Cirreversible toll of concussions on
OL,5,Crugby players
OL,7,F"I wouldn't be at all surprised if
OL,8,Fhe'd had 30, 35 concussions," Andrew
OL,9,Fsaid.
OL,11,F"Where sport needs to get real is that
OL,12,Fevery hit harms. It's not just the
OL,13,Fclear knockout blows. Every hit has an
OL,14,Fimpact."
OL,16,F"CTE (Chronic Traumatic Encephalopathy
OL,17,F- a brain condition caused by repeated
OL,18,Fhead trauma) is a disease of mileage.
OL,19,FAnd sport has to look to reduce that
OL,20,Fimpact on the brain for players."
