OL,7,FAs Cae's rugby playing days wound
OL,8,Fdown, he concentrated on his other
OL,9,Fcareer as a self-employed gas fitter.
OL,11,FBut he became more and more frustrated
OL,12,Fat his inability to complete tasks he
OL,13,Fwould previously have found simple.
OL,15,F"I suppose one of the most notable
OL,16,Fones for me was when he was working on
OL,17,Fhis boiler, connecting it up", Andrew
OL,18,Frecalls.
OL,26,@wD@AOUyD@]O]
