OL,3,C'Every hit has an impact': the
OL,4,Cirreversible toll of concussions on
OL,5,Crugby players
OL,7,FBy 2016, Cae was reaching a crisis
OL,8,Fpoint, even checking himself into a
OL,9,Fmental health unit.
OL,11,FSensing something was seriously wrong,
OL,12,FAndrew visited him at his home.
OL,14,F"He hadn't slept for four days, he was
OL,15,Freally struggling with anxiety,
OL,16,Fcouldn't switch off, he didn't even
OL,17,Fwant me to be there.
OL,26,@vD@AOU
