OL,3,C'Every hit has an impact': the
OL,4,Cirreversible toll of concussions on
OL,5,Crugby players
OL,7,F"I'd sort of forced myself upon him to
OL,8,Fbe there because it didn't seem right
OL,9,Fto me. And 2 or 3 days after that he
OL,10,Ftook his life."
OL,12,FCae was 37.
OL,14,FAndrew says it took time for his
OL,15,Ffamily and friends "to put the pieces
OL,16,Fof the puzzle together" and understand
OL,17,Fhow a man who'd once had such "clear
OL,18,Fand robust thought processes" could
OL,19,Fdecline so rapidly.
