OL,3,C'Every hit has an impact': the
OL,4,Cirreversible toll of concussions on
OL,5,Crugby players
OL,7,FBut with the growing publicity around
OL,8,Fhead injuries in sport, they started
OL,9,Fto draw the link between concussion
OL,10,Fand Cae's symptoms.
OL,12,FAnd Andrew isn't alone in thinking
OL,13,Fthat some in the game still aren't
OL,14,Ftaking the problem seriously enough.
OL,16,FGwyn Lloyd is the WRU Competitions
OL,17,FCoordinator for the Dragons region,
OL,18,Fresponsible for organising rugby
OL,19,Fcompetitions for senior and junior
OL,20,Fplayers.
