OL,3,C'Every hit has an impact': the
OL,4,Cirreversible toll of concussions on
OL,5,Crugby players
OL,7,FHe says he and his officials enforce
OL,8,FWelsh Rugby Union concussion protocols
OL,9,F- including mandatory 3 week layoffs
OL,10,Ffor players who've suffered a head
OL,11,Finjury.
OL,13,FBut some still try to bend the rules.
OL,15,F"In junior rugby in particular,
OL,16,Fparents are reluctant to take their
OL,17,Fchild off after they've had a bang on
OL,18,Fthe head."
OL,26,@wD@AOUzD@JO]
