OL,3,C'Every hit has an impact': the
OL,4,Cirreversible toll of concussions on
OL,5,Crugby players
OL,7,F"In some of the competitions we've
OL,8,Fhad, we've had conversations with
OL,9,Fcoaches who've said 'does he have to
OL,10,Fcome off?.'
OL,12,F"But at the level below professional
OL,13,Frugby there is no Head Injury
OL,14,FAssessment, it's 'Recognise and
OL,15,FRemove.'
OL,17,F"And if you're in doubt, "sit them
OL,18,Fout" for 21 days. Because the after-
OL,19,Feffects can be relentless."
