OL,7,FAlan Rideaux, the First Aider at
OL,8,FBedwas Barbarians rugby club near
OL,9,FCaerphilly, has dealt with several
OL,10,Fconcussions this season.
OL,12,FHe says he won't let players return to
OL,13,Fthe field if they're still showing
OL,14,Fsymptoms, even after they've served
OL,15,Fthe 3 week layoff.
OL,17,FThis can mean he has to withstand
OL,18,Fpressure from coaches and the players
OL,19,Fthemselves.
