OL,3,C'Every hit has an impact': the
OL,4,Cirreversible toll of concussions on
OL,5,Crugby players
OL,7,F"We do have pressure and in the end
OL,8,Fyou go back to the rules - the rules
OL,9,Fare the rules."
OL,11,F"You've just got to stand by the
OL,12,Frules. It doesn't matter what the
OL,13,Fcoach says, we've really got to focus
OL,14,Fon the player and nobody else."
