OL,3,C'Every hit has an impact': the
OL,4,Cirreversible toll of concussions on
OL,5,Crugby players
OL,7,FIn response, the Welsh Rugby Union
OL,8,Fsaid: "We work hard on providing
OL,9,Feducation throughout the community
OL,10,Fgame on concussion protocols... and we
OL,11,Fstrongly implore everyone involved...
OL,12,Fto adopt our 'if in doubt sit them out
OL,13,Fpolicy'.
OL,15,F"We proactively offer support...
OL,16,Faround concussion management.
OL,18,F"We also provide free first aid in
OL,19,Frugby courses to all clubs, with
OL,20,Fconcussion education embedded.
OL,26,@pD@GOUwD@AOUzD@AOU
