OL,3,C'Every hit has an impact': the
OL,4,Cirreversible toll of concussions on
OL,5,Crugby players
OL,7,F"There are a number of new resources
OL,8,Fwe have brought out this season (which
OL,9,Fare) available on... the WRU website."
OL,11,FBack in Cardiff, Andrew says he wants
OL,12,Fto see tougher rules around Head
OL,13,FInjury Assessments at the professional
OL,14,Flevel, and mandatory restrictions on
OL,15,Fcontact sessions outside of match.
OL,17,FHe also says he remains a big fan of
OL,18,Fthe game.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@apmqD@DpnqD@fO]
