OL,3,C'Every hit has an impact': the
OL,4,Cirreversible toll of concussions on
OL,5,Crugby players
OL,7,F"I'm a big believer in the positives
OL,8,Fthat rugby has. I'm not sitting here
OL,9,Fsaying that I want to ban sport. I've
OL,10,Fplayed rugby and it's got a hell of a
OL,11,Flot to offer to a lot of people.
OL,13,F"However, parents need to be aware of
OL,14,Fthe impact on young, developing
OL,15,Fbrains."
OL,17,FMost of all, he hopes Cae's story can
OL,18,Fhelp prevent further needless deaths
OL,19,Fin future.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOUwD@HO]
