OL,3,C'Every hit has an impact': the
OL,4,Cirreversible toll of concussions on
OL,5,Crugby players
OL,7,F"I don't think anyone really
OL,8,Fappreciated how much he was struggling.
OL,10,F"Looking at it now, the only option is
OL,11,Fto use this to raise awareness.
OL,13,F"And Cae's family certainly wouldn't
OL,14,Fwant to see any person go through what
OL,15,Fthey've gone through."
